  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You perform a brutal assault, beginning with a strong slashing attack and following up with a kick meant to send your opponent soaring backward. Make a melee Taijutsu attack, dealing your weapon's damage + 3d6 on a hit. Regardless of a hit or miss, you then kick the target. They must make a Strength saving throw, being knocked back 30 feet on a failure or half as much on a success.</p><p>After this initial attack, you command your Pod to create two solid light duplicates of itself, which then follow through with supercharged energy beams. Your Pod makes three Ranged Taijutsu attacks against the target creature, dealing its weapon's damage on a hit.</p><p>If two or more attacks would hit, the creature must then make a Wisdom saving throw, falling prone and becoming Blinded until the start of your next turn.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d6.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
